OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunshine and showers across
OL,6,Fmuch of the country, some heavy with
OL,7,Fhail and thunder. A drier and brighter
OL,8,Finterlude is possible across some
OL,9,Fwestern areas, ahead of thickening
OL,10,Fcloud and outbreaks of rain arriving
OL,11,Fhere by late afternoon. Average
OL,12,Ftemperatures.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers easing across eastern
OL,15,Fareas. Rain turning heavy in the west
OL,16,Fand spreading eastwards across all
OL,17,Fareas overnight. Turning increasingly
OL,18,Fwindy, especially over the hills and
OL,19,Faround the coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
