OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FRain quickly clearing to
OL,6,Fleave a day of sunshine and frequent
OL,7,Fshowers. Showers will be heavy at
OL,8,Ftimes, with hail and thunder.
OL,9,FRemaining rather breezy. Temperatures
OL,10,Faround average once again.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
